        <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 3.8rem; margin-bottom: 5px;">The Rescue Mission</h1>
        <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0; font-style: italic; opacity: 0.9;">Reconstructing the Authentic Voice of Mah Laqa Bai</p>
